product_desc:
We are a refreshing alternative to the traditional models in which veterinary care is delivered and will launch in San Francisco's Bay Area.
  Our network of veterinary hospitals will utilize technologies, communication and efficiencies to give pet owners what they want: a comprehensive, yet affordable and convenient, veterinary service that empowers them as members of their pet's healthcare team.
  At the heart of our success will be our Team, who will be freed from traditional workplace conditions such as low pay and long hours.  Stressing work life balance, collaboration and creativity our Team will be free to do what they do best: provide veterinary healthcare.
  In the end pet owners and Team members will work together to ultimately provide quality veterinary care to more patients
name: Veterinary Outpatient Network
